{
  "id": "adv_event_2410_01_05_02",
  "title": "パラダイス",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ライブ終了後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――After the live ended",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 1.2160586898,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05-skr013.m4a",
      "text": "ライブ、終わっちゃったね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The live is over…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.0960607195,
      "endTime": 5.1506638670000005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 5.3627273862
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "あんなに一杯考えて、沢山時間をかけて作り上げた\nライブなのに……始まったらあっという間だったわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We thought so much about it and spent so much time creating\nthis live‚ but… once it started‚ it was over in a flash.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.3627273862,
      "endTime": 14.3154936139,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.5283054972
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05-skr014.m4a",
      "text": "直前に思いついて急いで用意したサプライズ\nプレゼントもなんとか間に合って良かったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The surprise present we thought of at the last minute and hurriedly prepared\nsomehow made it in time‚ which was good.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.5283054972,
      "endTime": 21.464360013,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.6616388305
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "そうね、今日来てくれたみんなが\n帰り道にあれを見て、笑顔になってくれたらいいわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right‚ I hope everyone who came today\nwill see that on their way home and smile.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.6616388305,
      "endTime": 29.2495302184,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.4623421018
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05-skr015.m4a",
      "text": "……ライブ、楽しんでもらえたかな？\n感謝の気持ちは、ちゃんと届いたかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I wonder if everyone enjoyed the live?\nWould our feelings of gratitude properly reach them?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.4623421018,
      "endTime": 39.6832491223,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11804.324564899996
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 17237.657898200003
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 14404.324564899998
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.8956754351
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "ちゃんと届いてるわ\nだってほら、会場の拍手が全然鳴り止まないじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They properly reached them.\nLook‚ the applause from the venue isn't stopping at all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.8956754351,
      "endTime": 46.9208226824,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47.1336345657
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05-skr016.m4a",
      "text": "……本当だ\nみんなの拍手の音がここまで聞こえてくるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You're right.\nI can hear everyone's applause all the way here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.1336345657,
      "endTime": 56.2144058212,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.4003012324
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "地元っていいわね。今日のイベントで私達にとって\n星見市は特別なんだって改めて思ったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hometown is nice. Through today's event‚ I realized once again\nthat Hoshimi City is special to us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.4003012324,
      "endTime": 66.8509817745,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.0637936577
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05-skr017.m4a",
      "text": "この街のみんなの想いに応えられるように\nこれからもアイドルとして輝いていかないとね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So we can respond to everyone's feelings in this city\nwe have to keep shining as idols.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.0637936577,
      "endTime": 74.6935670838,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.8971269911
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "……今日のライブ、本当に楽しかった\n忘れられない思い出がまた一つ増えたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Today's live was really fun.\nAnother unforgettable memory has been added.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.8971269911,
      "endTime": 84.0146557158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.2274675991
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05-skr018.m4a",
      "text": "そうだね。ファンのみんなにとっても\n忘れられない日になってたらいいな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right. I hope it became\nan unforgettable day for all the fans too…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.2274675991,
      "endTime": 90.9098256733,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.0941342658
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05-skr019.m4a",
      "text": "ねぇ、琴乃ちゃん\nいつかまた、ここで里帰りライブをやろうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ Kotono-chan.\nLet's do a homecoming live here again someday.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.0941342658,
      "endTime": 98.50907777009999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.6941342658
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05-ktn014.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、いつかまた、この街で、この場所で……\n一緒に、里帰りライブをしましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ someday again‚ in this city‚ at this place…\nLet's do a homecoming live together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.6941342658,
      "endTime": 108.2889865227,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.3000241374
    }
  ]
}